subject: meta-supermicro: remove unusable x11spi machine
commitMessage:
meta-supermicro: remove unusable x11spi machine

This machine is unbuildable and has not been updated in the requisite 2
months per https://lore.kernel.org/openbmc/YRUW7cazmCjW8VpP@heinlein/,
so it is being deleted.

Signed-off-by: Patrick Williams <patrick@stwcx.xyz>
Change-Id: If06d6d5f8742445c4ed4a2654ab4ddc69f07db0b
